Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}就是这么回事{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's what's wrong!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}我的天啊{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, my.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 怎么了？ - 她想跟你碰面{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- What?     - She wants to meet you in person.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}听着 菲比 我本来也很想跟她碰面{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Look, Phoebe, I wanted to meet her in person too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}但她结婚了 她有丈夫{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But she's married. She has a husband.{\r}
